                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vous mîtes votre bras adroit,\nUn soir d’été, sur mon bras… gauche.\nJ’aimerai toujours cet endroit,\nUn café de la Rive-Gauche ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Au bord de la Seine, à Paris :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Un homme y chante la Romance",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Comme au temps… des lansquenets gris ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Vous aviez emmené Clémence.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Au bord de la Seine, à Paris :\nUn homme y chante la Romance\nComme au temps… des lansquenets gris ;\nVous aviez emmené Clémence."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Vous portiez un chapeau très frais",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Sous des nœuds vaguement orange,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Une robe à fleurs… sans apprêts,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Sans rien d’affecté ni d’étrange ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vous portiez un chapeau très frais\nSous des nœuds vaguement orange,\nUne robe à fleurs… sans apprêts,\nSans rien d’affecté ni d’étrange ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Vous aviez un noir mantelet,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Une pèlerine, il me semble,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Vous étiez belle, et… s’il vous plaît,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Comment nous trouvions-nous ensemble ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vous aviez un noir mantelet,\nUne pèlerine, il me semble,\nVous étiez belle, et… s’il vous plaît,\nComment nous trouvions-nous ensemble ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "J’avais l’air, moi, d’un étranger ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Je venais de la Palestine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "À votre suite me ranger,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Pèlerin de ta Pèlerine.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J’avais l’air, moi, d’un étranger ;\nJe venais de la Palestine\nÀ votre suite me ranger,\nPèlerin de ta Pèlerine."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Je m’en revenais de Sion,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Pour baiser sa frange en dentelle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Et mettre ma dévotion",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Entière à vos pieds d’Immortelle.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je m’en revenais de Sion,\nPour baiser sa frange en dentelle,\nEt mettre ma dévotion\nEntière à vos pieds d’Immortelle."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Nous causions, je voyais ta voix",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Dorer ta lèvre avec sa crasse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Tes coudes sur la table en bois,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Et ta taille pleine de grâce ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Nous causions, je voyais ta voix\nDorer ta lèvre avec sa crasse,\nTes coudes sur la table en bois,\nEt ta taille pleine de grâce ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "J’admirais ta petite main",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Semblable à quelque serre vague,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Et tes jolis doigts de gamin,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Si chics ! qu’ils se passent de bague ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J’admirais ta petite main\nSemblable à quelque serre vague,\nEt tes jolis doigts de gamin,\nSi chics ! qu’ils se passent de bague ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "J’aimais vos yeux, où sans effroi",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Battent les ailes de votre Âme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Qui font se baisser ceux du roi",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Mieux que les siens ceux d’une femme ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J’aimais vos yeux, où sans effroi\nBattent les ailes de votre Âme,\nQui font se baisser ceux du roi\nMieux que les siens ceux d’une femme ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Vos yeux splendidement ouverts",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Dans leur majesté coutumière…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Étaient-ils bleus ? Étaient-ils verts ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Ils m’aveuglaient de ta lumière.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vos yeux splendidement ouverts\nDans leur majesté coutumière…\nÉtaient-ils bleus ? Étaient-ils verts ?\nIls m’aveuglaient de ta lumière."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Je cherchais votre soulier fin,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Mais vous rameniez votre robe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Sur ce miracle féminin,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Ton pied, ce Dieu, qui se dérobe !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je cherchais votre soulier fin,\nMais vous rameniez votre robe\nSur ce miracle féminin,\nTon pied, ce Dieu, qui se dérobe !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Tu parlais d’un ton triomphant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Prenant aux feintes mignardises",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "De tes lèvres d’amour Enfant",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Les cœurs, comme des friandises,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tu parlais d’un ton triomphant,\nPrenant aux feintes mignardises\nDe tes lèvres d’amour Enfant\nLes cœurs, comme des friandises,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "La rue où rit ce cabaret,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Sur laquelle a pu flotter l’Arche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Sachant que l’Ange y descendrait,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Porte le nom d’un patriarche.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La rue où rit ce cabaret,\nSur laquelle a pu flotter l’Arche,\nSachant que l’Ange y descendrait,\nPorte le nom d’un patriarche."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 14,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Charmant cabaret de l’Amour !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Je veux un jour y peindre à fresque",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Le Verre auquel je fis ma cour.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Juin, quatre-vingt-cinq, minuit… presque.",
